{"type": "article", "id": 15717, "title": "Zippo 打火机", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-08T07:24:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003326BltS4Q3UrTn2Kv1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国的打火机品牌 Zippo（芝宝）专门生产具有一定收藏价值的金属打火机。近期邀请英国时装设计师 Christopher Shannon 设计了一组非常酷炫的“外衣”，一共 4 套，风格迥异但兼具强烈的时尚感。它们其实是设计师 2016 春夏系列的服装，相互配合也有互相宣传的作用。售价 40 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.shopchristophershannon.com/shop\" target=\"_blank\">这里是预购链接。 </a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143113xMgCvKbaY7P6chZ9.jpg\" width=\"1010\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74257426\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143113QPTmOvhdz6eUxE91.jpg\" width=\"1013\" height=\"757\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74728529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143114OUZFCfwS6WmIR82B.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"749\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}